-   <span data-ttu-id="dd84d-106">Чтобы получить сведения о текущих операциях распознавания речи, подпишитесь <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechDetected>на <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechHypothesized> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer>события <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechRecognitionRejected>,, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechRecognized> и.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dd84d-106">To get information about current speech recognition operations, subscribe to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer>'s <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechDetected>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechHypothesized>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechRecognitionRejected>, and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechRecognized> events.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="dd84d-107">Чтобы просмотреть или изменить число альтернативных результатов, возвращаемых распознавателем, используйте <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.MaxAlternates%2A> свойство.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dd84d-107">To view or modify the number of alternate results the recognizer returns, use the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.MaxAlternates%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="dd84d-108">Распознаватель возвращает результаты распознавания в <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognitionResult> объект.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dd84d-108">The recognizer returns recognition results in a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognitionResult> object.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="dd84d-109"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevel%2A>Чтобы получить доступ или отслеживать состояние общего распознавателя, используйте <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.State%2A> свойства, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.RecognizerAudioPosition%2A> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioPosition%2A>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioState%2A> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.PauseRecognizerOnRecognition%2A> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.Enabled%2A> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioSignalProblemOccurred>,,,, и ,,<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevelUpdated> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioStateChanged>события и <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.StateChanged> .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="dd84d-109">To access or monitor the state of the shared recognizer, use the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevel%2A>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioPosition%2A>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioState%2A>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.Enabled%2A>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.PauseRecognizerOnRecognition%2A>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.RecognizerAudioPosition%2A>, and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.State%2A> properties and the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevelUpdated>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioSignalProblemOccurred>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioStateChanged>, and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.StateChanged> events.</span></span>  
  
